GET /api/flows
  List all flows (filter by variant, domain, regulatory flags)
  Query: ?domain={domain}&variant={HAPPY_PATH}&regulatory={GDPR}
  Response: BusinessFlow[]

POST /api/flows
  Create a new flow (UI-driven or YAML import)
  Body: BusinessFlow { id, name, steps[], endToEndSlo, ... }
  Response: BusinessFlow (201)

GET /api/flows/{id}
  Fetch flow with complete step details
  Response: BusinessFlow { steps, criticalPath, asyncLegs, ... }

PUT /api/flows/{id}
  Update flow (steps, SLO, ownership)
  Response: BusinessFlow

GET /api/flows/{id}/variants
  List all variants of this flow (DEGRADED_MODE, COMPENSATING, CANARY)
  Response: BusinessFlow[]

POST /api/flows/{id}/variants
  Create a variant (derived from parent)
  Body: { variant: "DEGRADED_MODE", parentFlowId: id }
  Response: BusinessFlow (201)

GET /api/flows/{id}/health
  Current SLO status of this flow
  Response: { p99Latency, errorRate, sloStatus, criticality }

POST /api/flows/{id}/test
  Trigger integration test for this flow
  Response: { testId, status, results[] }
